data.title: Tegan and Sara Archive
data.meta_description: An fan-made archive of content and information about Tegan and Sara.
data.text:
This website was made to document the history of the band and is intended to be a resource for anyone looking for content and information about Tegan and Sara. It is made by fans and is not affiliated with Tegan and Sara or anyone else mentioned on this website. Each page on the menu will have more information about what you can find there.

This website is a work in progress and is consistently being updated with new information and content. Feel free to let me know any feedback you have about the site or if you think anything is incorrect or if something should be added or removed. Please note that photos, videos, audio, and articles are hosted on this site only if they have not been made available by the original source. If it can be found online, it is linked to rather than hosted on the site. All sources and credit are given if that information is known. No copyright infringement is intended and if I posted anything that is yours and you would like for me to take it down, please contact me and I will do so as soon as possible.
